  <summary>Messenger for the desktop</summary>
  <metadata_license>CC0-1.0</metadata_license>
  <url type="homepage">https://getferdi.com/</url>
  <url type="bugtracker">https://github.com/getferdi/ferdi/issues</url>
  <url type="help">https://getferdi.com/contact</url>
  <description>
    <p>
      Ferdi is a messaging browser that allows you to combine your favorite messaging services into
      one application. It is based on Franz - a software already used by thousands of people - with
      the difference that Ferdi gives you many additonal features and doesn't restrict its usage!
    </p>
    <p>
      Ferdi is compatible with your existing Franz account so you can continue right where you left off.
      Find out more about Ferdi and its features on getferdi.com. 
    </p>
  </description>
